---
const highlights = [
  'Curated drops that feel personal, not algorithmic noise.',
  'Purpose-built for students & young professionals chasing value.',
  'Backed by ethical commerce, transparent pricing, and bold design.',
];
---

<header class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-night via-night/95 to-night/60">
  <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col gap-10 px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
    <nav class="flex items-center justify-between text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-slate-300">
      <span class="font-semibold text-white">Shievon</span>
      <span class="text-fire">Alpha Access · 2025</span>
    </nav>

    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="space-y-8">
        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-rose-100">
          Commerce first. Culture always.
        </p>
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase text-fire">Reinvent. Rebuild. Rise.</p>
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold leading-tight text-white sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
            A fire-powered marketplace rewriting how the bold shop, sell, and show up.
          </h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-200">
            Shievon is a multi-vertical platform with e-commerce at its core—fueling creators, rebels, and misfits with
            curated drops, trust-first logistics, and immersive buying moments.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-300">
            {highlights.map((item) => (
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-2.5 w-2.5 flex-none rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-fire to-ember"></span>
                <span>{item}</span>
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="#cta"
              class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-fire/30 bg-fire px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white shadow-lg shadow-fire/30 transition hover:translate-y-0.5 hover:bg-fire/90"
            >
              Join the movement
            </a>
            <a
              href="#marketplace"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/15 px-6 py-3 text-base font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-white/80 transition hover:text-white"
            >
              Explore the marketplace vision
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-6 rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10"></div>
        <div class="relative rounded-[2.5rem] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-6 shadow-2xl shadow-fire/10 backdrop-blur">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-fire to-ember p-6 text-white">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-white/70">Marketplace Engine</p>
            <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-semibold">Phoenix Commerce Stack</h2>
            <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/90">
              Drop intelligence, zero-friction checkout, and verified seller pods engineered for scale.
            </p>
            <dl class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-white/90">
              <div>
                <dt class="opacity-70">Curated verticals</dt>
                <dd class="text-2xl font-semibold">12+</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="opacity-70">Community sellers</dt>
                <dd class="text-2xl font-semibold">4.8k</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="opacity-70">Drop velocity</dt>
                <dd class="text-2xl font-semibold">45s</dd>
              </div>
              <div>
                <dt class="opacity-70">Trust score</dt>
                <dd class="text-2xl font-semibold">98%</dd>
              </div>
            </dl>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl bg-night/70 p-4 text-slate-200">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.4em] text-fire">Roadmap</p>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Layer two pillars—careers and social impact—on top of the marketplace backbone to create the Shievon
              trilithic ecosystem.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-300">
              <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Commerce</span>
              <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Consultancy</span>
              <span class="rounded-full border border-white/10 px-3 py-1">Social</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

